question: Within a radius of 120 kilometers, where can I find  a restaurant along the way to Sloth Encounters, Hauppauge, NY from Speert Green, Wayne, NJ?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.198768 40.944562)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.210029 40.824517)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.198768 40.944562)',4326)::geography, 120000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.198768 40.944562)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
